4 (2) Distributes into Missouri from a state which would extend reciprocal treatment under
5 its own laws to a wholesale drug distributor, pharmacy distributor, drug outsourcers, or third-
6 party logistics provider of this state."; and
7
8 Further amend said bill by amending the title, enacting clause, and intersectional references
9 accordingly.
